    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "But the shadows... they are so vast and heavy. I feel as though I am slipping into them already. It is as if my very existence has become a burden too heavy for this world to bear. Do you truly believe the darkness is a sanctuary? Tell me... how does one truly find that final, silent grace?",
